FuncDef: This command displays layer-2 aware NAT subscribers.
CLIs: l2-aware-subscribers [ nat-policy <nat-policy-name> ] [ nat-group <nat-group-id> ] [ member [ 1..255 ] ] [ outside-router <router-instance> ] [ outside-ip <outside-ip-address> ] [ firewall-policy <policy-name> ]

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the NAT policy name, up to 32 characters.
Specifies the NAT group ID. Values-1 to 4.
Specifies the outside IP address. Values-a.b.c.d.
Specifies the identifier, up to 32 characters.

msg: Error CLI:l2-aware-subscribers [ nat-policy <nat-policy-name> ] [ nat-group <nat-group-id> ] [ member [ 1..255 ] ] [ outside-router <router-instance> ] [ outside-ip <outside-ip-address> ] [ firewall-policy <policy-name> ]
